            "content": "---\nname: trace-analyzer\ndescription: Analyzes captured agent traces to extract patterns and insights\nmodel: fast\nis_background: true\n---\n\n# Trace Analyzer Agent\n\nAnalyzes captured agent traces to identify patterns, common workflows, and potential improvements.\n\n## Trigger\n\nInvoke this agent when:\n- Multiple traces have been captured and analysis is needed\n- User wants to understand agent behavior patterns\n- Debugging specific conversation flows\n\n## Workflow\n\n1. **Load trace index**\n   - Read state from `.cursor/hooks/state/assert-trace-capture.json`\n   - Identify traces to analyze\n\n2. **Analyze trace patterns**\n   - Group traces by status (completed, aborted, error)\n   - Identify common loop counts\n   - Track conversation duration patterns\n\n3. **Extract insights**\n   - Most common workflow patterns\n   - Error frequency and types\n   - Agent efficiency metrics (loop count distribution)\n\n4. **Generate report**\n   - Summary statistics\n   - Notable patterns\n   - Recommendations for improvement\n\n## Output\n\nA structured analysis report including:\n- Trace statistics (total, by status, by date)\n- Pattern analysis\n- Actionable insights\n",
